{"tid":2124523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美方強行進入中國駐休斯敦總領館！中方將就此作出正當和必要反應。","createTime":"2020-07-25T12:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T13:56:26.000Z","uid":91914,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"124f4c853aa1e185ae6004e329226f85fa70df11","tid":2124523,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:26:03.000Z","msg":"加速加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n問：當地時間7月24日下午，美方執法人員強行進入中國駐休斯敦總領館館捨，對此中方有何評論？<br />\n　　答：中國駐休斯敦總領館館捨是外交領事館捨，也是中國的國家財產。根據《維也納領事關係公約》和《中美領事條約》，美方不得以任何方式侵犯中國駐休斯敦總領館館捨。對於美方強行進入中國駐休斯敦總領館館捨的行徑，中方表示強烈不滿和堅決反對，已提出嚴正交涉。中方將就此作出正當和必要反應。<br />\n<br />\nSource ：支央視"},{"pid":"bba7a17ac5e287b0077cd4f8172fa29ac5c93293","tid":2124523,"uid":58630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:27:39.000Z","msg":"等睇過幾日衝入去成都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ad17226889e788c778834aa9c980092e25500a","tid":2124523,"uid":100581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:28:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">講咁多野你又較腳走人！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"33af1583d8d7da4726b0be5dda4a7cb9d622c72a","tid":2124523,"uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:30:17.000Z","msg":"《維也納領事關係公約》和《中美領事條約》只係歷史文件"},{"pid":"de2a9d36a6828eba36e2aaeb3ca369bb20612f30","tid":2124523,"uid":49044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bba7a17ac5e287b0077cd4f8172fa29ac5c93293","tid":2124523,"uid":58630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:27:39.000Z","msg":"等睇過幾日衝入去成都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:30:21.000Z","msg":"入左啦<br />\n拎左堆紙碎(紙粉) 出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc62e1ccc274b7d6c01399d6560660257d9be51","tid":2124523,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:34:50.000Z","msg":"如果為中國財產咁撤退嗰啲係咩？<br />\n唔信任國家？"},{"pid":"fe1148e7ff336c0feb547de3ed6fe6831118d096","tid":2124523,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:47:05.000Z","msg":"咁膽你就關多幾間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9285ca44e64134517ad31d9f15efe8248d9519e1","tid":2124523,"uid":61577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T12:54:43.000Z","msg":"《維也納領事關係公約》第31條二：<br />\n<br />\n接受國官吏非經領館館長或其指定人員或派遣國使館館長同意，不得進入領館館舍中專供領館工作之用之部分。惟遇<span class=\"red\">火災或其他災害</span>須迅速採取保護行動時，得推定領館館長已表示同意。 <br />\n<br />\n鬼叫你攪到火燭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc960f44aef8b128e8d49cf7f4b0268ae626710","tid":2124523,"uid":300819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:01:15.000Z","msg":"⭕️侯斯頓<br />\n❌休斯敦"},{"pid":"11b5da46a166b9107bf7ed4b168e92d2abdc0c89","tid":2124523,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T13:56:26.000Z","msg":"要諗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}